rows.label: qst200915_msg002
rows.name: I-I had a terrible time, mo...

rows.label: qst200915_msg003
rows.name:
And it's all Kasane's fault, mo! Ever
since the old days, nothing good happens
when I get involved with you, mo!

rows.label: qst200915_msg004
rows.name:
After I parted with you,
I fell off a cliff...

rows.label: qst200915_msg005
rows.name:
I was attacked by the Tirkin
tribe and had my cargo stolen,
it was the worst, mo!

rows.label: qst200915_msg006
rows.name:
It was an important delivery
for today, how are you going
to take responsibility, mo!

rows.label: qst200915_msg017
rows.name:
Is that the ingredients to be
delivered to Tuuli Bakery?

rows.label: qst200915_msg018
rows.name:
Yes, mo! But now I don't have
a single thing left, mo!

rows.label: qst200915_msg007
rows.name: Now, now, please calm down a bit, mo...

rows.label: qst200915_msg008
rows.name:
It's alright, Kupon-san.
Please leave it to us!

rows.label: qst200915_msg009
rows.name:
Thanks to the Lucky Sachiveria
Bread, we're in top form right
now. We'll solve everything!

rows.label: qst200915_msg010
rows.name: That's why! This is all your fault...

rows.label: qst200915_msg013
rows.name:
No, anyway, if you can get it
back from the Tirkin tribe,
that's all that matters, mo.

rows.label: qst200915_msg015
rows.name: Can I really trust you, mo?

rows.label: qst200915_msg014
rows.name:
Then, everyone, for Kupon-san's
sake, let's head to the Tirkin
territory once more!
